query:
SELECT
                l1_batch_number,
                chain_id,
                status,
                protocol_version,
                protocol_version_patch
            FROM
                proof_compression_jobs_fri
            WHERE
                (l1_batch_number, chain_id) = (
                    SELECT
                        MIN(l1_batch_number),
                        chain_id
                    FROM
                        proof_compression_jobs_fri
                    WHERE
                        status = $1
                        OR status = $2
                    GROUP BY chain_id
                )
